CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FMore British troops are being sent to
OL,7,Fthe Middle East to help UK allies
OL,8,Fdefend their skies from Iranian
OL,9,Fattacks as the conflict continues to
OL,10,Fescalate.
OL,12,FSpeaking during a trip to Gulf
OL,13,Fnations, Defence Secretary John Healey
OL,14,Fsaid the UK will deploy the Sky Sabre
OL,15,Fair defence missile system in Saudi
OL,16,FArabia and extend UK Typhoon jets'
OL,17,Faction in Qatar.
OL,19,FAdditional air defence teams and
OL,20,Fsystems have also arrived in Bahrain
OL,21,Fand Kuwait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FHealey did not give specific figures,
OL,7,Fbut said "Britain's best" will be
OL,8,Fchosen for the missions as he visited
OL,9,FSaudi Arabia, Qatar and Bahrain.
OL,11,FSky Sabre ` a Royal Artillery battery
OL,12,Fand battle space managers who operate
OL,13,Fthe system ` will be moved to Saudi
OL,14,FArabia this week.
OL,16,FThe defence system, composed of
OL,17,Fradars, a control node, and missile
OL,18,Flaunchers, can intercept munitions and
OL,19,Faircraft.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FIt will be integrated into broader
OL,7,FSaudi and regional air defences,
OL,8,Faccording to the Ministry of Defence
OL,9,F(MoD).
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAs he met UK troops at Qatar's Dukhan
OL,17,Fairbase, Healey confirmed British
OL,18,FTyphoons will continue their action in
OL,19,FQatar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FThe Royal Air Force's joint Typhoon
OL,7,Fsquadron with Qatar deployed to the
OL,8,FGulf in January amid rising tensions
OL,9,Fin the region, and Prime Minister Sir
OL,10,FKeir Starmer announced the dispatch of
OL,11,Ffour more of the fighter jets to the
OL,12,Fstate earlier this month.
OL,14,FHealey thanked pilots who have been
OL,15,Fconducting flying missions over Qatar,
OL,16,FBahrain, Jordan, and the United Arab
OL,17,FEmirates since the start of the US-
OL,18,FIsrael war against Iran more than a
OL,19,Fmonth ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FGulf nations have borne the brunt of
OL,7,FTehran's retaliation, with thousands
OL,8,Fof Iranian missiles and drones
OL,9,Ftargeting US military sites and energy
OL,10,Finfrastructure.
OL,12,FBritish pilots operating Typhoon, F-
OL,13,F35, Wildcat and Merlin helicopters
OL,14,Fhave exceeded more than 1,280 flying
OL,15,Fhours in the Middle East, according to
OL,16,Fthe MoD.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FHealey also said on Tuesday that the
OL,7,FUK's Lightweight Multirole Launcher
OL,8,Fhas arrived in Bahrain, supported by a
OL,9,Fteam of UK experts who will help
OL,10,Fintegrate the short-range air defence
OL,11,Fsystem into Bahraini defences.
OL,13,FRapid Sentry, a ground-based short-
OL,14,Frange missile launching weapon, is now
OL,15,Fin Kuwait, where the RAF's
OL,16,Fcounterdrone Orcus system is also
OL,17,Fallowing soldiers to detect Iran's
OL,18,FShahed drones early.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FHealey said: "Iran's aggressive
OL,7,Fattacks continue to threaten our
OL,8,Fallies and interests in the Middle
OL,9,FEast.
OL,11,F"That's why the UK has been flying
OL,12,Fdefensive missions since day one of
OL,13,Fthis conflict to protect British
OL,14,Finterests and allies ` and today we're
OL,15,Fdelivering further support by
OL,16,Fextending our UK jets in Qatar and
OL,17,Fdeploying extra air defence teams and
OL,18,Fsystems to the Kingdom of Saudi
OL,19,FArabia, Bahrain and Kuwait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,F"I am proud of the courage and
OL,7,Fprofessionalism our armed forces have
OL,8,Fshown since the start of the war, and
OL,9,Fmy message to Gulf partners is:
OL,10,FBritain's best will help you defend
OL,11,Fyour skies.
OL,13,F"I pay tribute to the heroic efforts
OL,14,Fof our partners across the Gulf in
OL,15,Fprotecting their nations.
OL,17,F"We will stand by our long-term
OL,18,Fpartners in the Middle East and
OL,19,Fcontinue to push for a swift
OL,20,Fresolution to this conflict."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775045470
OL,3,CMore UK troops will be sent to Middle
OL,4,CEast to help defend Gulf allies
OL,6,FThe Defence Secretary met the Emir of
OL,7,FQatar, the King of Bahrain and defence
OL,8,Fleaders from all three nations during
OL,9,Fhis trip.
OL,11,FThey discussed the conflict, further
OL,12,FUK-Gulf co-operation on regional
OL,13,Fsecurity, and Iran's selective
OL,14,Fblockade of the vital oil and gas
OL,15,Fshipping route the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,16,Fwhich alongside its attacks on Gulf
OL,17,Fnations has pushed up global energy
OL,18,Fprices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
